  "detailed_description": "Tantal is a cunning collector who dreams of collecting coins and crystals. In the game you collect coins, crystals and solve crystal puzzles.<br> <br>The game takes place in the \"T\" world!<br>Tantal is obsessed with finding rare crystals and loves to solve logic problems.<br> <br>Game features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast travel<br></li><li>Solving puzzles like in a match 3 game)<br></li><li>Collect coins, everyone loves coins<br></li><li>Collecting crystals<br></li><li>Puzzles through the mechanics of the game three in a row<br></li><li>Limited number of moves</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425280/extras/3e9ae2cfd3d987530b30da4e71cfd075.poster.avif?t=1662893331\" width=520 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425280/extras/3e9ae2cfd3d987530b30da4e71cfd075.webm?t=1662893331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425280/extras/3e9ae2cfd3d987530b30da4e71cfd075.mp4?t=1662893331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A - The number of points scored.<br>B - The number of moves left.<br>C - The number of points required to move to a new level.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425280/extras/069a20827ab9d7144acc930ed519c9dc.avif?t=1662893331\" width=616 height=840 /></span>",
